				\begin{document}$$V_{\rm SCref} = 40\,V$$\end{document}. As a first stability criterion, the first Lyapunov method is used. This method assess the eigenvalues of the Jacobian of the vector field:30JZD=∂x˙3∂x3∂x˙3∂x4∂x˙4∂x3∂x˙4∂x4(x3,x4)=(75,40).\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
